//Recursive factorial function  
~factorial-n_*n&<=&1:if_!return-1_:else_*n&-&1@prev!factorial-prev@prevfact*n&*&prevfact@result!return-result__

//Test factorial with different values
*5@input
!factorial-input@result
!alert-"Factorial of"-input-"is"-result

*0@zero
!factorial-zero@zerofact
!alert-"Factorial of"-zero-"is"-zerofact

*10@ten
!factorial-ten@bigfact
!alert-"Factorial of"-ten-"is"-bigfact
